  "text": "We presented a model to naturally introduce SVD feature selection in a probabilistic taxonomy learner. The method is effective as allows the designing of better probabilistic taxonomy learners. We still need to explore whether or not the positive effect of SVD feature selection is preserved in more complex feature spaces such as syntactic feature spaces as those used in [CITATION_1] .",
